Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:06.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,刚开始练习骑车带人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,适应被她抱着可费功夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很危险的 不要挠我痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我没有挠你痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是轻轻抓住你而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:38.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的腰很怕痒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是你的手弄得太痒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,换个姿势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:44.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:47.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太近了 你靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但不这样的话很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说 你很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:55.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:58.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 靠太近会很热嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之 不要抱太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明你刚才还说「抓紧了」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:12.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们来试试看哪种抓法比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:24.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你快点 练习的时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:30.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:34.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,克服了重重困难 终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样就掌握骑车带人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 这样就结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:53.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你都掌握了如何骑车带人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就没必要继续特训了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:02.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你会觉得寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:06.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还是说你终于松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:10.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不寂寞好像不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要说寂寞感觉会被她捉弄得更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,两边都有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学又是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我应该不会寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:37.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天去图书馆补作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来对答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:52.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,相对的 第二学期要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,台风真的会来吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,台风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,风好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,飞得好高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真不愧是台风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心里突然来劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,风啊 来得更猛烈些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这感觉 就像是我把风吹起来了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,风啊 听从我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,风好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我把头发扎起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我刚才看了一下风向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我还什么都没问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:47.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么总在不想被她看见的时候被看见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以 你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以说 我在看风向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我还以为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,风啊 来得更猛烈些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定在这样玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:09.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,客观来看还真是羞耻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但你为什么要看风向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是不知道风向会很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 毕竟风这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是像这样把双手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:30.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 就像是我把风吹起来了一样 爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家会以为你在这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好羞耻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:39.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 我和之前有什么不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没骑自行车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你觉得我为什么没有骑自行车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那当然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:00.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就不告诉别人西片在对着台风自个儿爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 都说了那是在看风向…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要在那个袋子被吹到这边之前回答哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有时间限制吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一定要想办法猜出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:15.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,故意问出来 肯定有小心思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:21.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,应该不是因为风太大骑车危险这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,仔细想想 仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,除了风太大以外 能让她为难的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,自行车 风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是裙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这么害臊的东西怎么说得出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:52.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,答案是风太大 骑车很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快走吧 该去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,风好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总感觉很兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不觉得想要放飞自我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:29.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,张开双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喊着「哇哈哈 风啊 来得更猛烈些吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「我正操纵着疾风」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「现在的我是支配着整个世界的风之王者」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「能把学校吹飞到世界的另一端」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:49.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「哈哈哈哈哈哈哈」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才没有想那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然不是在看风向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们跑去学校吧 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,风好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么老是那么狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:16.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}感觉今天早上的高木同学 心情非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,马拉松
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好嘞 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还真是精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不是很讨厌跑马拉松吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 我很期待马拉松的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗 和我一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我赢了 你中午就不许吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没问题 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗跑得超快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我肯定不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要跑马拉松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:57.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明平时连几十分钟都没跑过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:00.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么非得去干这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你好像很有干劲嘛 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的要比吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这可是我提出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们在交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:36.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是输的人要听胜者命令的比赛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要在马拉松比赛啊你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:46.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,的确感觉他们不像是在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要说正在交往的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你状态怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,多亏了你每天陪我一起训练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,应该是那样子才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么一定要去跑步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还是死心吧 木村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心无旁骛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错 要排除杂念地跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:33.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为了不浪费体力 一心无二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 你上当了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为了这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我连续两周以上的傍晚都在跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:47.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不管风吹雨打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:51.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以 我不可能会输给她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:56.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 专心 专心跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我以为你会冲在更前面的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:05.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把握节奏才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看来你是不懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然你看起来还有余力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:17.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但肯定是因为看不见我着急得加快脚步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想着让一下你 刚才都在慢慢地跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说她竟然读懂了我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:39.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要没有午饭吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:43.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我冲得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:48.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,跑那么快的话 待会肯定会喘不过气的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只要保持现在的节奏就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学很擅长跑马拉松吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是那样的话就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在可不是胡思乱想的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她已经跑回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然有女生跑得比男生还快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然节奏被打乱了 但还是追上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片能碰到我 那就算你赢好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:41.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能在众目睽睽之下去碰高木同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样 可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然扰乱了我的节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:58.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你能和我拉开五十米以上的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就算你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:07.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这次轮到我来扰乱高木同学的节奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接招吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,女生在这里折返哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}女生在这里折返
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,男生的折返点还有两公里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都提醒过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂西片 不要停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:40.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 果然会肚子疼 会肚子饿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,跑马拉松什么的 哪里有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:47.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是把你抱怨的精力都用在跑步上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就能跑得再快一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才不想干那种没有意义的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:55.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,跑步和说话 哪边更没意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我 我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,侧腹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天也被她捉弄得够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总有一天我会报复回来的 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的侧腹真的很怕挠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一有机会就会这样干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然我的侧腹很怕挠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道还有人不怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不要来比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,规则是谁先笑谁输
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:46.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 我准备要说开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:50.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,上钩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你没有看清局势啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学正推着自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,腾不出双手 局势非常不利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:06.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这样子怎么能保护自己的侧腹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的侧腹不怕痒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哇 你忍住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但她竟说自己的侧腹不怕痒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是在骗我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么她浑身上下都是破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说真的不怕痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:46.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之只要试一试就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉好害臊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的可以戳她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,会不会被当做是性骚扰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不上的话 又轮到我进攻了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我还觉得是个完美的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没想到还有这样的陷阱在里头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,风险太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:28.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在应该和她保持距离 算作平局好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:43.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 你的表情太犯规了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你笑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了 我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学还有鬼脸这一必杀技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要让你干什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 还有惩罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是当然的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一辈子不许吃大米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,开玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,禁止看百分百单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样好像也太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你戳我的侧腹看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:45.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就是惩罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:03.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她是打算让我害羞不敢碰她来取乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才不会让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:15.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说 我好像还是第一次去碰高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不要想无关的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要戳她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:34.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错吧 我侧腹不怕痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:46.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,腋下倒是很怕痒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谁敢碰那种地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:58.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:02.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好了 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假时没去试胆大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放学的时候去一趟吧 不去不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是灵异地点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的要进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:33.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这不是参加试胆大会的反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是油桶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么什么 为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,完全不吓人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:04.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是吗 难道不吓人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:05.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是飞盘 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像好凉快 是不是鬼怪作祟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是白天比较通风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不要追着我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们玩够没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:39.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,非常有暑假的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:46.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:54.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假已经一去不复返了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:02.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,别突然就低沉下来啊 真烦人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:15.04,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:25.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:34.19,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:42.45,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.41,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:50.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.71,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:06.72,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:14.98,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:20.40,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:24.41,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:34.67,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.62,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:15.04,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:25.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:34.19,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校园的庭院 第一个发现你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:42.45,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你说些什么呢 即便是想着这些也是一种乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.41,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗帘随风起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:50.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不经意地投入一束阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.71,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美丽的容颜笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.59,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:06.72,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿喧嚣 似要吹散考试的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:14.98,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 我想要和你一起 立下两人的秘密约定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:20.40,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:24.41,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:34.67,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:12.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}はっきり言って努力は嫌いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.86,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}はっきり言って人は人だね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:25.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどなぜ窓ガラスに映る姿気にしてるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:32.24,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどなぜ意地になって　移る流行気にしてるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}はっきり言ってお伽話は罠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:44.84,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}期待したってカボチャはカボチャ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:51.68,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどもうダメみたいだ　何だか近頃おかしいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:59.02,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどもうダメみたいだ　何だか近頃おかしいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.73,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}走り出した足が止まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:07.07,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}行け　行け　あの人のところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.86,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}誰にも抜かれたくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:13.20,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風　風　背中を押してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.75,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}足が止まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:19.96,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}行け　行け　あの人のところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:22.71,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}誰にも負けたくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:26.38,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風　風　背中を押してよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:12.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}说实话 我最讨厌的就是努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.86,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}说实话 别人就是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:25.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但为什么我会在意自己映在玻璃窗上的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:32.24,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但为什么意气用事地在意着不断变化的流行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}说实话 童话故事都是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:44.84,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}就算如何期待 南瓜也还是南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:51.68,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但好像有点不行了 感觉最近的自己有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:59.02,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但好像有点不行了 感觉最近的自己有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.73,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}疾驰的脚步无法停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:07.07,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}去吧 去吧 到那个人的身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.86,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不希望被任何人超越
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:13.20,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿 风儿 助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.75,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}脚步无法停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:19.96,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}去吧 去吧 到那个人的身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:22.71,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不希望输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:26.38,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿 风儿 助我一臂之力
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
